    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美丽的生存恐怖 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152440/extras/409c7230c2fc8e3cb01e914d4160be33.poster.avif?t=1771019163\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152440/extras/409c7230c2fc8e3cb01e914d4160be33.webm?t=1771019163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152440/extras/409c7230c2fc8e3cb01e914d4160be33.mp4?t=1771019163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>几十年来，生存恐怖游戏始终是一个无可比拟的传奇品类，向世界各地的玩家带去了无穷乐趣。《绝命花》正是秉承了这个游戏类型的传统，通过紧张的玩法、烧脑的谜题和令人惊艳的美术，向大家展现全新的游戏设计。生死与成长的故事  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152440/extras/54e7b444f12003405d50e63a21534325.poster.avif?t=1771019163\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152440/extras/54e7b444f12003405d50e63a21534325.webm?t=1771019163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152440/extras/54e7b444f12003405d50e63a21534325.mp4?t=1771019163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >杰西卡·帕克来湖滨小镇乔伊克里夫原本只是为了送花，谁知致死的疫病席卷了这里，她短暂的行程陷入了一片混乱。这个疫病导致花草疯长，夺取人命，并将死者变成了狰狞的怪物。只有她这个幸存之人知道怎样拯救大家，也只有她有勇气揭穿这些骇人事件背后的阴谋。乔伊克里夫已然变成了花园地狱，她必须奋力求生，杀出一条路来。游戏简介</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152440/extras/8f32273a7b9e30b31069aee1e148cf51.poster.avif?t=1771019163\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152440/extras/8f32273a7b9e30b31069aee1e148cf51.webm?t=1771019163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152440/extras/8f32273a7b9e30b31069aee1e148cf51.mp4?t=1771019163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>- 固定视角，增强紧张氛围，展现精致的美术设计<br>- 各类敌人不断演化，只等你去发现、战胜<br>- 各式谜题考验你的洞察力、推理能力和脑洞<br>- 威力强大的爆炸性 武器等你发现<br>- 游戏世界随着剧情推进会不断生长、变化<br>- 没有背包管理，看到什么就拿什么，拿到什么就用什么<br>- 开发团队身体里流淌的都是“生存恐怖”的血液</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《绝命花狱》将于2026年全球同步推出，敬请期待！欢迎将游戏加进愿望单，分享给好友，也欢迎进入官方Disocrd社群，与其他玩家和开发团队畅谈！</p>",
